      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine and a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This specimen is mechanically superlative: the VANOS unit has been comprehensively serviced, and the rear subframe has undergone proactive reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The individual throttle bodies (ITBs) provide instantaneous transient response, while the variable M differential lock ensures precise power delivery out of the apex. Finished in original paint with zero oxidation, the chassis remains as tight as the day it left Regensburg. This is a turn-key, collector-quality example for the enthusiast who demands peak naturally aspirated performance without compromise.",
